The MyGuichet.lu app enables you to:
•	carry out certain administrative procedures and keep track of their progress directly from your smartphone and/or tablet;
•	add supporting documents to your procedures;
•	consult your communications with administrations; 
•	access certain personal and/or professional data that is held by the Luxembourg authorities.

GouvID allows you to:
- add your ID card information to an electronic wallet;
- authenticate yourself with an online public service;
- sign documents presented in the context of these services;
- change the initial PIN of your ID card after its issuance;
- change the current PIN of your ID card.

Luxauto is the number one intermediate for used cars/motorbikes in Luxembourg and the Greater Region (France, Belgium and Germany).
This iPhone app helps you, just as easily as on the site www.luxauto.lu, to find what you are looking for among professional and private ads. 
Features:
- fast and detailed search among over 10.000 ads which have been checked by a car specialist before;
- memorizing of interesting and/or relevant ads;
- saving among preferences/favourites;
- direct mail or phone contact with the seller; 
- look-up of the ads of the day.
